<para>File descriptor specifying the audio file. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">auto_destroy</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>If true, the sound output is destroyed when playback reaches end of file. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">dynamic_decode</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Not currently implemented. </para>
